reviews.text:
I have been twice and enjoyed it very much! The chicken is just perfect without too much grease or batter. It is definitely bar with bar food around dinner time, but chill and not over crowded.

We also enjoyed the 치즈 해물 떡볶이 (seafood with rice cakes in hot sauce gratiné). It was spicy, but exactly as it should be.

Been here several times already. Come here mainly for the delicious fried chicken. Crispy on the outside and tender on the inside. Limited choices on the menu though. Portion is big. Service is not good either.

Restaurants that serve Korean crusine . They lunch menu during lunch hours and happy hour menu for evening. Food are delicious, partilcular reasonably priced lunch sets. Deep fried chicken is a must try for the place.

Lunch here is nice, the set lunch box with great variety of food, and size is big, definitely can fill you stomach.
And the taste is good, not like traditional Korean food, but still seasoned with great taste.
Restaurant is noisy, and tables are packed.  Not comfortable to stay for chat.
Staffs are nice, but not enough manpower during lunch peak hours

result.name: 李家

reviews.text:
今日同朋友突然好想食韓國野，就決定搵下有咩平靚正既餐廳。
比我地發現到呢間李家（灣仔店），睇佢門口有點舊，利用了較深色的玻璃，阻擋了陽光的透入，令人覺得有點神秘的感覺。

入到店入內，店員都好親切的輕輕介紹。
店內的套餐都有不小的款式烤牛、牛排、豬肉。當然唔少石頭飯、雜錦煲，真係睇到都流口水了。

後來發現，原來仲有一張午餐精選，果然叫精選，入面有水冷麵、拌飯、海鮮拉麵等等...（呢張更像韓國的午餐）

餐廳內部裝潢簡單，但水吧位比較多物品

而地方尚算整潔，座位都比較鬆動，位與位唔會太擠迫。

烤特級牛肉 - $68
一來到，我終於知道自己點解突然想食韓國野啦，貪佢前菜已經有好多唔同的野食，細數最少有5-6款加泡菜，仲有沙律，而且更有一碗清清地的菜湯。

烤牛肉食落不會太韌及出現多筋的情況，醬汁醃過的牛肉更包鎖著了其肉味，性價比高。:like:
一個叫雞但唔只叫雞既地方！黑到睇電話覺得會盲！
